{"tid":1842218,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥稱醫護不應激進爭取訴求","createTime":"2020-01-25T14:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:47:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b80551b2230a9cf19928374cf8a3f27ad29f9442","tid":1842218,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200125/_2020012518120061368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200125%2F_2020012518120061368.jpg&h=d2c7761f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥召開記者會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200125/_2020012520080826981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200125%2F_2020012520080826981.jpg&h=a7a7a585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200125/_2020012520080950718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200125%2F_2020012520080950718.jpg&h=4b39c20f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200125/_2020012520081063442.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200125%2F_2020012520081063442.jpg&h=8fbf7fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥指封關是不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n有醫護人員聲稱如果政府不封關或者拒絕內地旅客入境就發動罷工，行政長官林鄭月娥表示， 如果為了防疫封閉所有跟內地連接的關口，是不切實際，指有關旅客亦可以走到其他地方，再進入香港，強調不封關，不是有政治考慮。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，醫護人員不應該用激進行爭取訴求，明白醫護人員有情緒，但應該開心見誠去討論。可能過去7個月大家習慣了用激進手段去表達，但大家應該和平理性。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人揣測衞生署長陳漢儀一般社交場合無需戴口罩言論與禁蒙面法有關，林鄭月娥反駁是不尊重陳漢儀專業立場，不相信陳漢儀會想得這麼遠。林鄭月娥指，在任何情況和場合戴口罩亦未嘗不可，但亦要考慮防疫效益，重申人流密集地方，本身身體不舒服或屬照顧者，提供公共服務等，都是理想做法。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強調，有關上訴裁決，與是否呼籲全民戴口罩的公共衛生議題無關，指政府提出上訴，與禁蒙面法沒太大關係，而是尋求法庭確立緊急法本身，在憲制上屬有效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1688502/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%87%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B-%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1688502%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%25BF%2580%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJaHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=e6bda87f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1688502%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%2587%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%259A%259B-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%25BF%2580%25E9%2580%25B2%25E7%2588%25AD%25E5%258F%2596%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582&h=3f2a839a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1688502/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E7%A8%B1%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%87%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B-%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E6%BF%80%E9%80%B2%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82</a>"},{"pid":"53446ecd25d1dbfd71e2b0f30664fec042b9fa84","tid":1842218,"uid":336046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"香港市